Created by FontForge 20170924 at Wed Dec 10 06:20:40 2008 By Glenn,,, Designed by Sean Cavanaugh for FontSite.com, CombiNumerals Ltd is the free version of CombiNumerals Pro. This limited version provides a unique and elegantly simple method for creating encircled numbers of one or two digits. To create circled numbers with more digits -- as well as decimal values, super and subscripts, currency symbols, alphabetic characters and more (including numbers and letters enclosed within ovals, rectangles and other shapes) -- please refer to the commercial version of this font, CombiNumerals Pro.
For more information about the CombiNumerals family of fonts, please visit the FontSite online at http://www.fontsite.com
